  "prompt": "What is the average salary for an IT consultant in Dubai?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, the average salary for an IT consultant in Dubai typically ranges from AED 100,000 to AED 250,000 per year, depending on various factors such as experience, specialization, and the size of the company. Junior consultants may earn towards the lower end of that scale, while senior consultants or those with specialized skills can command higher salaries.\n\nFor the most accurate and up-to-date information, it's advisable to check local job listings, salary surveys, or reports from recruitment agencies in Dubai.",
